room_description:
The world's most infamous hacker, The Phantom, has finally been apprehended. Hiding in plain sight as a wealthy Scottish nobleman, the Phantom lived the life of luxury by day and modern day pirate by night. Before being caught, he created one of his most devious hacks ever, a virus that can cripple the entire internet as well as the code needed to restore it.
The Phantom planned to sell his virus to the highest bidder and now that he's incarcerated, every sinister organization on the planet is searching for it. Find the virus and anti-code before it falls into the wrong hands and the world falls back into the dark ages!
